; Coverage test for account.cc earliest/latest functions (L343-362).
; Exercises get_earliest (L343-345), get_latest (L352-354), and
; the 'e' case in lookup (L435-440).

2024/01/01 Grocery
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/02 Gas Station
    Expenses:Gas     $30.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/03 Grocery
    Expenses:Food    $5.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal --no-total --flat --format "%(earliest)|%(latest)|%(account)\n"
2024/01/01|2024/01/03|Assets:Cash
2024/01/01|2024/01/03|Expenses:Food
2024/01/02|2024/01/02|Expenses:Gas
end test
